4. RESTful API 接口规格4.1 素材摄取 (Parser 推送)URL: POST /api/v1/scripts/ingestPayload: ```json{"title": "如何用AI写代码","content": "...","sourcePlatform": "douyin","externalId": "123456","statistics": {"likes": 100, "shares": 50}}Success: 202 Accepted4.2 语义搜索爆款钩子URL: GET /api/v1/fragments/search?topic=职场&type=HOOK&limit=3Response: 返回语义最接近的 3 个 Hook 及其逻辑拆解。4.3 AI 文案创作 (Few-Shot)URL: POST /api/v1/compositions/generatePayload:JSON{
  "topic": "新产品发布",
  "sampleUuids": ["uuid1", "uuid2"],
  "options": {"tone": "幽默", "length": "300"}
}
5. 关键技术细节5.1 异步非阻塞处理利用 Java 21 的 Virtual Threads 配合 Spring @Async。AI 拆解是一个典型的 I/O 密集型任务，虚拟线程可以显著降低线程开销。Java// AsyncConfig.java
@Bean
public Executor taskExecutor() {
    return Executors.newVirtualThreadPerTaskExecutor();
}
5.2 Spring AI 提示词工程 (Few-Shot 组装)在生成文案时，系统会动态构造 Prompt：$$Prompt = System\_Role + User\_Topic + \sum (Reference\_Logic + Reference\_Content)$$Java// 简化代码逻辑
var samples = vectorStore.similaritySearch(request.topic());
String prompt = """
    你现在是爆款编剧。参考以下逻辑：
    %s
    请根据上述风格，为主题 %s 创作文案。
    """.formatted(samples, request.topic());
